msgstr "Sync-fijnafstelling"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2980
msgid "If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they play together."
msgstr "Loopt de Bluetooth-luidspreker nog achter op de bekabelde, verhoog dit tot ze samen spelen."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2992
msgid "Sync delay in milliseconds"
msgstr "Synchronisatievertraging in milliseconden"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3014
msgid "Type an exact delay in milliseconds — the slider moves in steps of ten."
msgstr "Typ een exacte vertraging in milliseconden — de schuifregelaar beweegt in stappen van tien."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3018
msgid "ms"
msgstr "ms"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3032
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Kalibreren met de microfoon"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3037
msgid "Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set automatically."
msgstr "Speelt een paar luide klikken door elke luidspreker en meet met de microfoon hoeveel de Bluetooth-luidspreker achterloopt — de vertraging wordt automatisch ingesteld."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3057
msgid "Round 1 of 2 — clicks through every speaker…"
msgstr "Ronde 1 van 2 — klikken door elke luidspreker…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3058
msgid "Round 2 of 2 — quiet, checking the result…"
msgstr "Ronde 2 van 2 — stil, resultaat wordt gecontroleerd…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3096
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 speelt in de groep"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3109
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Of deze luidspreker in de groep meespeelt — vink uit om hem over te slaan zonder de verbinding te verbreken. Onthouden voor het apparaat."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3118
msgid "%1 (nothing plugged in)"
msgstr "%1 (niets aangesloten)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3132
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Balans van %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3141
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "Het aandeel van deze luidspreker in het volume — de balans volgt elke beweging van de hoofdregelaar en wordt voor het apparaat onthouden. Hij werkt alleen op wat deze widget afspeelt; het volume per apparaat in de systeeminstellingen is een aparte, onaangeroerde laag — daarom wijken die getallen af van deze schuifregelaars."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3158
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3159
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3160
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
