msgstr "De Bluetooth-luidspreker loopt %1 ms achter — de vertraging is ingesteld en onthouden voor dit apparaat."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:415
msgid "Balance levels set earlier were replaced by the measured ones."
msgstr "Eerder ingestelde balansniveaus zijn vervangen door de gemeten niveaus."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:423
msgid "The microphone clipped on %1 — that balance was left unchanged; lower the speaker's volume and calibrate again."
msgstr "De microfoon sloeg over bij %1 — die balans bleef ongewijzigd; zet de luidspreker zachter en kalibreer opnieuw."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:424
